      "raw_text": "A deposition containing evidence to\nbe used on tho trial of the case of\nPeter Anderson and wife against the\nGreat Northern was received this morn\ning at the county clerks Office from\nthe United States consul at Chris\ntiania, Norway. The action is for\n$1,000 damages for the loss OF the life\nOF the plaintiffs son, Andrew Ander-\nson, by being run over by the cars OF\nthe defendant in April, 1902, at North\nport,"
